{"about_the_game":"Hex Party is a 4 player online and local-multiplayer party game. Compete in a board game full of epic friendship-wrecking minigames.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CROSS-PLATFORM MULTIPLAYER</h2>Play solo or up to 4 players both online or locally. You can play Hex Party with your friends using different platforms such as PC, Mac, Mobile and consoles.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179180/extras/5edited.jpg?t=1707688019\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">BOARD</h2>Compete with your friends in multi-themed boards and use your best tactics and items stay ahead of the game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179180/extras/Edited6.jpg?t=1707688019\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PERSONAL ITEMS</h2>Hex Party takes you to a steampunk universe full of magic and fun items. In addtion to treasure items found in chests, you can grab yourself a personal item from your favorite vampire shop that you can use multiple times using your energy.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179180/extras/2edited.jpg?t=1707688019\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">EPIC MINIGAMES</h2>Miss the golden age games from old ? Hex Party brings back a blast from the past with epic minigames inspired from your favorite childhood games. Hex Party minigames are longer, more complex and more fun.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179180/extras/SandKarts_Resized.jpg?t=1707688019\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179180/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1707688019","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179180/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1707688019","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstat